<li>We are here for you during this challenging period.</li>
<li>Our thoughts are with you and your family.</li>
<li>The team is here to support you in any way possible.</li>
<li>We extend our deepest condolences to you and your family.</li>
<li>We will miss (deceased's name)'s contributions to the team.</li>
<li>Please know that we are all thinking of you during this difficult time.</li>
